    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "丢了哪里找，光是焦急有什么用？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贤弟帮忙，老哥哥当然没话说，可是，这位——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位也不是外人，她是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是鬼面人，以后请老镖头多指教。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
